POD1000000022_S0000112	we're almost always being turned into pure facticity in other people's minds for example have you ever walk around in yourself conscious about the way you look maybe you just got a new pair of shoes and you think they look weird and as you're walking around you feel like every person that passes you is looking at you and they're thinking
